1
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:04,720
I heard that the phoenix fell from the west.

2
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:08,800
It looks like a heavenly sign.

3
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:11,680
Your Highness.

4
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:13,840
Long time no see.

5
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:15,440
How have you been?

6
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:18,360
How are you, General?

7
00:01:19,160 --> 00:01:20,280
But I'm different.

8
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,480
But a loser

9
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,280
There's no Phoenix.

10
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:26,480
Hahaha.

11
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:56,920
Your Highness, you're so beautiful.

12
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:59,080
and beautiful.

13
00:02:02,880 --> 00:02:06,160
The new and old emperors can't forget you.

14
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:08,600
Now,

15
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:12,080
the spies who are looking for the Empress Dowager are all over the country.

16
00:02:13,360 --> 00:02:14,560
Do you think

17
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:16,800
Should I hand him over or not?

18
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:20,920
If you hand me over,

19
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:25,520
I'll treat you as a true gentleman who is loyal and patriotic.

20
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,840
Am I

21
00:02:28,160 --> 00:02:29,920
loyal to the emperor and patriotism?

22
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,920
I like that Momo.

23
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:36,040
Ask her to serve my mother in her tent.

24
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:57,200
Baili Jinghong has evil intentions towards you.

25
00:03:00,760 --> 00:03:01,800
He has ulterior motives?

26
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:05,000
Tell me, why is he up to no good?

27
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:08,120
He's obviously coveting you.

28
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,000
You...

29
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:16,760
Why did you stop?

30
00:03:17,079 --> 00:03:18,240
I have nothing to say.

31
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:27,640
Huo Lingyu.

32
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:30,360
I have no choice.

33
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:37,880
Ji Hong Zhen ascended the throne

34
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:40,079
You want to imprison me as a caged bird?

35
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,600
If I don't want to surrender,

36
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:46,079
I can only get power.

37
00:03:46,920 --> 00:03:48,520
The supreme power.

38
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:50,880
In this world,

39
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:54,800
only Baili Jinghong can help me get this power.

40
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:58,040
I know he is a wolf.

41
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:01,040
But I have to fight a tiger for its skin.

42
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:06,640
Huo Lingyu.

43
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:09,040
Do you dare?

44
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,760
Together, we'll make a big scene.

45
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:12,560
Do you dare?

46
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,600
You...

47
00:04:15,920 --> 00:04:16,959
I'm asking you.

48
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:19,640
How dare you?

49
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:21,079
No.

50
00:04:21,079 --> 00:04:21,880
I dare.

51
00:04:30,840 --> 00:04:32,520
A wise master is not afraid of the danger of justice.

52
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,840
Only loyal officials deserve to die.

53
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:38,920
Give me five.

54
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,800
Never betray.

55
00:05:02,840 --> 00:05:03,640
Junior general.

56
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:28,360
We could have entrusted our lives

57
00:05:29,200 --> 00:05:30,880
and never betray.

58
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:39,880
and return to the city.

59
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:50,200
Baili Jinghong,

60
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:53,320
You want to use my identity to rebel.

61
00:05:54,360 --> 00:05:57,040
I want to use your military power to return to the capital.

62
00:05:57,800 --> 00:06:00,400
It depends on who is better at it.

63
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:08,080
Be careful, Your Highness.

64
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,480
Your Highness, this way please.

65
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:25,920
This way, please.

66
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,600
General likes lotus.

67
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:30,960
There happens to be a bunch of hot spring in this pond.

68
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:34,520
So you asked the gardener

69
00:06:34,760 --> 00:06:36,600
to adjust the water temperature.

70
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:39,280
It can make lotus bloom until winter.

71
00:06:40,280 --> 00:06:41,600
Your Highness is a distinguished guest.

72
00:06:41,840 --> 00:06:43,320
General has ordered

73
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:45,840
to let you stay in the Lotus Garden.

74
00:06:46,760 --> 00:06:49,800
You can come to the lotus rowing boat if you're free.

75
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:51,480
This place is quiet too.

76
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:55,159
No one will disturb you.

77
00:06:57,120 --> 00:06:58,120
Okay.

78
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,720
Where is your young general?

79
00:07:00,280 --> 00:07:01,280
Junior general.

80
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:03,280
I don't know.

81
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:04,880
Excuse me.

82
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:14,800
We failed to find the ledger.

83
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:17,920
There is false news from Mount Beili.

84
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,600
Two crimes shall be punished together.

85
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,880
As usual, Nine-head.

86
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:24,360
I’ll forgive you

87
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:26,040
I will forgive you.

88
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:33,080
He Lian Jin.

89
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:35,480
Who are you?

90
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:37,200
Shim Lian.

91
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:38,720
The Helian Clan

92
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:41,080
or Baili Jinghong?

93
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:36,559
I borrowed some white snow

94
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:39,679
I borrowed it from her.

95
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:43,720
Is my godson pretty?

96
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,240
Yes.

97
00:09:50,760 --> 00:09:52,160
Hahaha.

98
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:53,960
Nine-head.

99
00:09:54,480 --> 00:09:56,880
You’re still so brave.

100
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:01,400
General, what about these warriors?

101
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:07,280
I'm happy today.

102
00:10:08,160 --> 00:10:09,280
Don't kill him.

103
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:10,480
Keep it.

104
00:10:10,480 --> 00:10:11,080
Yes.

105
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,480
General, a military report.

106
00:10:41,920 --> 00:10:43,920
What did Baili Jinghong do to him

107
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:46,880
to make him so controlled?

108
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:48,720
Maybe

109
00:10:49,160 --> 00:10:50,840
can really be used by me.

110
00:10:54,960 --> 00:10:57,000
Junior general, are you alright?

111
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,240
I'm fine.

112
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:00,960
Give them the medicine.

113
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,800
Thank you for taking care of them.

114
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:04,160
My life is yours.

115
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:05,920
This is nothing.

116
00:11:08,520 --> 00:11:09,760
The general is getting more and more cruel.

117
00:11:10,440 --> 00:11:13,200
You earned all these military merits.

118
00:11:13,880 --> 00:11:16,120
but he's making fun of you.

119
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:19,360
When?

120
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:21,320
as long as you can be our general.

121
00:11:21,600 --> 00:11:22,960
Go apply medicine on them.

122
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:24,280
Yes.

123
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:46,120
I told you not to leave the bandits' den.

124
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:47,320
but you wouldn't listen.

125
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,200
When Moo-yeol met you on the North Gorge Mountain,

126
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:51,040
There's nothing he wouldn't tell you.

127
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:53,920
We sent fake news so frequently.

128
00:11:54,440 --> 00:11:55,320
I knew it.

129
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:57,080
You will be punished as soon as you come back.

130
00:11:57,440 --> 00:11:58,760
You haven't recovered from your previous injury.

131
00:11:59,160 --> 00:12:00,840
Now there's a new wound.

132
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,680
I'll get a doctor.

133
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,040
I'm fine.

134
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:15,600
Have you

135
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:16,680
to see General Shen?

136
00:12:17,040 --> 00:12:17,840
Yes.

137
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:19,760
But it's not good.

138
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:23,120
The doctor said General Shen is dying.

139
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,560
There's not much time left.

140
00:12:28,280 --> 00:12:29,560
Looks like we need to know

141
00:12:29,880 --> 00:12:31,440
what he did to her

142
00:12:32,040 --> 00:12:33,280
to find a solution.

143
00:12:45,680 --> 00:12:46,640
Good.

144
00:13:27,040 --> 00:13:27,840
Soldiers.

145
00:13:28,880 --> 00:13:30,360
Let's drink.

146
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:39,080
Her Highness is here.

147
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:41,640
You bastards!

148
00:13:41,640 --> 00:13:44,640
You don't even bow and kneel when you see Her Highness.

149
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:47,920
Your Highness.

150
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:49,160
It doesn't matter.

151
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:52,120
Please step back.

152
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,760
Why?

153
00:13:55,560 --> 00:13:57,160
Let's eat.

154
00:13:57,160 --> 00:13:58,400
Be generous.

155
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:01,560
You should get used to it.

156
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,240
Fine.

157
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:07,360
Let's talk about the Royal Seal.

158
00:14:10,280 --> 00:14:12,280
General, I've asked around.

159
00:14:12,280 --> 00:14:14,160
The royal seal was indeed lost.

160
00:14:14,680 --> 00:14:15,640
What?

161
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:20,240
Get out of here!

162
00:14:27,520 --> 00:14:29,120
The new emperor has ascended the throne.

163
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:31,560
It's justifiable.

164
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:33,440
No one in the court

165
00:14:34,280 --> 00:14:35,800
no one ever heard

166
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:38,320
the late emperor had another will.

167
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:41,160
I know

168
00:14:41,760 --> 00:14:43,040
I know.

169
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:46,600
the border will send troops to the capital.

170
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:47,760
is a taboo.

171
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:50,280
If you are not careful,

172
00:14:50,280 --> 00:14:53,440
you'll be accused of treason.

173
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:02,720
Do you think you caught me?

174
00:15:05,920 --> 00:15:06,720
No.

175
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:09,400
I chose you.

176
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:12,960
Because I chose you.

177
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:15,200
That's why I'm standing by your side now.

178
00:15:16,200 --> 00:15:17,160
and slander you for treason.

179
00:15:18,520 --> 00:15:19,600
Baili Jinghong,

180
00:15:20,680 --> 00:15:22,680
Are you afraid?

181
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:33,680
The new emperor loves me.

182
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:36,240
He's crazy.

183
00:15:36,920 --> 00:15:38,800
If I want wealth and power,

184
00:15:39,120 --> 00:15:40,440
I'll have everything.

185
00:15:41,680 --> 00:15:43,840
Why do you think I want to escape from the palace?

186
00:15:54,560 --> 00:15:56,840
Hahaha.

187
00:15:57,800 --> 00:16:00,720
You've got guts.

188
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,040
Demon Queen, stop!

189
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:14,520
You're so arrogant.

190
00:16:14,800 --> 00:16:16,440
I thought she was so noble.

191
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:19,720
But she's a bitch who tried to seduce our general.

192
00:16:20,080 --> 00:16:21,920
She is indeed a shameless demon queen.

193
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:24,080
Now you're bringing it up again.

194
00:16:26,200 --> 00:16:27,240
What did you say?

195
00:16:28,920 --> 00:16:29,880
What are you glaring at?

196
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:31,680
Am I wrong?

197
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:35,280
Who knows how you became the Empress Dowager?

198
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,920
First, the Emperor, then the Crown Prince.

199
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:40,440
Now you're thinking about our general.

200
00:16:43,080 --> 00:16:44,520
If you say one more word,

201
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:46,640
I'll pull out your tongue.

202
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:53,640
Prepare water. I want to take a bath.

203
00:16:53,640 --> 00:16:54,440
Okay.
